{"tid":2150799,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美資行封高官戶配合制裁  彭博：兩大型中資行亦評估風險","createTime":"2020-08-11T05:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T06:03:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0802661ea2573420130e365a503c623e64cc3a","tid":2150799,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/E3HXPRV7IIMCUSBTBWWQFQTNDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FE3HXPRV7IIMCUSBTBWWQFQTNDY%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lEt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=8ba5aa6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FE3HXPRV7IIMCUSBTBWWQFQTNDY%2F&h=0811623a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/E3HXPRV7IIMCUSBTBWWQFQTNDY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美資行封高官戶配合制裁 <br />\n彭博：兩大型中資行亦評估風險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DT6_EoyMPsnpdFrYrxHKryeIJnA=/1088x709/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DREQIIKSGRR3SBSU3Y3IP7GDJU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDT6_EoyMPsnpdFrYrxHKryeIJnA%3D%2F1088x709%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDREQIIKSGRR3SBSU3Y3IP7GDJU.gif&h=3c255a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國上周宣佈制裁包括特首林鄭月娥在內的11名中港官員。設計圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國上周宣佈制裁11名中港官員，與之往來的銀行接下燙手山芋，亦展開「掃雷」行動，否則財政部第二輪制裁清單將劍指金融機構。彭博引述消息謂，最少一間美資行已暫停被制裁官員賬戶；有不具名銀行業人士亦向本報分析，相關對象被列入美國最頂級制裁級別（SDN），面對壓頂風險，相信大部份金融機構都會採取「寧枉毋縱」的最嚴格合規尺度處理。<br />\n<br />\n彭博報道亦指，另外有兩間大型中資銀行，正就其風險承受能力及合規要求。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上周五美國對中港高官實施的制裁不設過渡期，意即立時實行，財政部在未來。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n被問及是否彭博報道所指的美資行，花旗銀行發言人回覆說，不會就個別客。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或間接對聯滙帶來風險<br />\n<br />\n大和資本首席經濟師賴志文發表報告表示，制裁官員的名單公佈後，「現在壓力來到銀行」，投資者要注意，因尚未與制裁對象。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一位不願具名的銀行界主管說，由於11名中港官員被列入等同國際罪犯的。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n該名銀行界主管又稱，因應目前國際局勢變化，尤其國際性銀行會考慮其他。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨黨魁鍾國斌出席一個電台節目稱，美國對中港官員制裁主要是一種表。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"06386203435907a98dc3db69a163f114517dcdc1","tid":2150799,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lEt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=1c475bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},{"pid":"a363858fcce689bb3e9ee9fe24afce228e9116ed","tid":2150799,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdb677c501db026911979997d4b39e7980d34cd","tid":2150799,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecdced55a298116d15dc58b7be73d963d74f7e3","tid":2150799,"uid":37739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b46242b60fa6c4b107d2855866d1fe1e39d12a","tid":2150799,"uid":156073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as